# Interactive prompts — respond to stdin questions
# Prompts are pipe-based: works with programs that read line-by-line from stdin
# (shell read, PHP fgets, Python input(), Symfony Console, etc.)
# Programs requiring a PTY (sudo, passwd, ssh) are NOT supported.
@timeout 3000
sh examples/interactive_script.sh
EXIT 0
[Prompts]
"Enter username:" => "alice"
"Enter email:" => "alice@example.com"
/Confirm\?/ => "y"
[Asserts]
stdout contains "Created user: alice <alice@example.com> (confirmed: y)"
